data.description: Calling all Investors.  Don't miss out on this traditional split style home sitting on large lot over 3/4 acre in a well established neighborhood with NO HOA!  This super spacious home has so much potential and would be perfect to renovate and keep as a rental. Finish the basement for even more living space.  Offers will need to be cash or renovation loan, because home needs lots of work, including replacing HVAC. This is an amazing location just in to Paulding county from Cobb County.  With no rental restrictions and no HOA, the possibilities are endless. Just minutes to Lake Allatoona and lots of shopping and restaurants.  Motivated seller - bring offers.
